  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Evaluate the net force on a current loop in an external magnetic field</item>
<item>Evaluate the net torque on a current loop in an external magnetic field</item>
<item>Define the magnetic dipole moment of a current loop</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
